#eliandmike #mikeygarcia

How do you MANIFEST your 5 year FUTURE? 🔮

What you want most doesn’t happen overnight. You have to work hard everyday for years before you get to your destination. Quick exercise: I want you to take a seat and jot down what exactly the future you in 5 years looks like. 📝

Now that it’s visible, manifest it and execute on it. This is what our great friend Mikey Garcia @teammikeygarcia is doing. Creating wealth from poverty. You can always change your stars if you can just focus a bit more and stop being so lazy. Yes you will fall, but realize it doesn’t happen to you it’s happening for you. 📈
